718771f-a.title: Manhattan: Chittenden Avenue - 187th Street (West)
718771f-a.text:
Chittenden Avenue, at about West 187th Street, view
ing eastward up slope to same atop the retaining wall.
April 30, 1924
Standard Photographic Service
Gift of Borough President of Manhattan

718772f-a.title: Manhattan: Chittenden Avenue - 187th Street (West)
718772f-a.text:
Chittenden Avenue, at about W. 187th Street, view
ing northward. At the left is the Hudson River.
April 30, 1924
Standard Photographic Service
Gift of Borough President of Manhattan
